Eve: Eh, I'm kinda irritated with humanity at the moment. I just got out from Jacob's and, apparently, this little guy here was dumped off and abandoned by their owner. 

(Pipo moment)

Trace: Whaaaat? Who'd ever want to throw a cutie with a face like that to the curb??

Eve: Right?! My thoughts exactly! Uhg, it grinds my gears that some people can be so heartless.

Trace: You got a plan for housing 'em?

Eve: Depends. Do you want a cat?

Trace: Sure! :D

Eve: ... I was kidding, are you serious?

