Eve: Point taken. The cat's yours.

Trace: Yay. I'll call them... Pipo...

Eve: ...You're gonna name them after the sound of their meow?

Trace: You named your dog after a breakfast item. I don't want to hear it.

Eve: Touche.

(Trace giggle sprite)

Trace: Well given this turn of events, it looks like I'll need some supplies. Mind making the journey to Marnie's with me?

Eve: Sure, you're gonna get lost if I don't come with you anyways.

Trace: Such cruelty. I have no idea how you ever came to that conclusion.

Eve: Can it, princess. Let's go.

